^ pray for the government trying to solve the crisis b. . 
^ pray that it would be solved in a way which helps all the people of the country 
^ c. . 
^ pray for the big companies , that they would be aware of their responsibilities towards their employees d. . 
^ pray that foreign investors would not be shunned away because of the situation 
